title: Scrapbook, 1998-75-115, 1920–50
inscribed: INscribed on album front cover: Historical Houses Containing Old Wallpaper Designs Reproduced by Nancy McClelland
creditline: Gift of The Museum at The Fashion Institute of Technology
description: Containing old wallpaper designs reproduced by Nancy McClelland, including Mount Vernon, Jumel Mansion, Governor Lucas House, Brompton, Stanton Hall, House of History, Wadsworth-Longfellow House, Folsom Tavern, Gore Place, Connecticutt Valley Historical Society, Wadsworth Antheneum, and Continental Hall.
